            (cmp_valid == CmpValid) && ((down_cnt + up_cnt_q[0]) != {1'b0, max_val}) |-> err_o)
    `ASSERT(CrossCntErrBackward_A, err_o |->
            (cmp_valid == CmpValid) && ((down_cnt + up_cnt_q[0]) != {1'b0, max_val}))

